                Deanae <lb n="2"/>in <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>pro iuventute <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivitatis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sum</abbr><ex>elocennensis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Her<lb break="no" n="5"/>mes <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Verschollen; angeblich 2 Fuß (circa 60 cm) hoch und 1,5 Fuß (circa 45 cm) breit. (B): Z. 3: pr[o]; Z. 4/5: H[e]r/mes [f.].</p>
            </div>
